results.name: Square array 7 x 7 read by rows.
comment: Permutation contributing to the determinant that gives the 7th value of the Möbius function. Determinant of matrix is equal to -1. The array is symmetrical.
link: Herbert S. Wilf, The Redheffer matrix of a partially ordered set, arXiv:math/0408263 [math.CO], 2004.
results.author: _Mats Granvik_, Sep 13 2008
